and we still managed
to win the war.

03:08.222 --> 03:10.255
Can you please stop
with these stories?

03:10.257 --> 03:11.823
This is a real life
situation here.

03:11.825 --> 03:14.459
Dad, we gotta get
a second phone line.

03:14.461 --> 03:15.327
