in your underpants.

03:57.504 --> 03:58.170
It's disconcerting.

03:58.172 --> 04:00.672
It's like you're trying
to drive people away.

04:00.674 --> 04:02.708
That's because
I am trying to
drive people away.

04:02.710 --> 04:05.210
Well, that is why
you have no friends, Murray.

04:05.212 --> 04:06.578
I live in a house
full of people

04:06.580 --> 04:08.714
who won't leave me
the hell alone.

04:08.716 --> 04:10.015
That's all the friends
I need.

04:10.017 --> 04:13.252
