want friends, but I do.

04:13.254 --> 04:14.486
Go over there and apologize

04:14.488 --> 04:16.622
for being a pantsless
grumpy pants.

04:16.624 --> 04:19.725
(SPOON CLINKS)
I should apologize
for being me?

04:19.727 --> 04:21.760
Yes!
(DOORBELL RINGS)

04:22.996 --> 04:27.032
Hi. I'm, uh, Murray Goldberg
from across the street.

04:27.034 --> 04:30.602
