I'd come over and
formally introduce myself.

04:30.604 --> 04:33.138
Charles Kremp.
Pleasure to meet you.
Come on in.

04:33.140 --> 04:34.806
Oh, okay. Thank you.

04:34.808 --> 04:37.342
