04:39.113 --> 04:41.780
It's a perk of the job.
I'm a florist.

04:41.782 --> 04:42.748
Oh, how about that?
That's right.

04:42.750 --> 04:47.653
We have a flower spray
that we keep in
the bathroom.

04:47.655 --> 04:49.388
It tries.

04:49.555 --> 04:51.089
But the point is,

04:51.091 --> 04:53.692
I am here to invite you
to a barbecue.

04:53.694 --> 04:56.361
Yes, that...
That situation.

04:56.363 --> 04:59.698
So... It is
a situation, huh?

04:59.700 --> 05:01.300
From now on,

05:01.302 --> 05:04.002
I will try and, uh,

05:04.004 --> 05:06.238
wear pants
when I go outside.

05:06.240 --> 05:06.972
Try.

05:06.974 --> 05:10.876
To be honest, um,
my... my wife Virginia,

05:10.878 --> 05:16.915
she can be
a little sensitive,
and, uh... (CHUCKLES)

05:16.917 --> 05:20.085
How to put this...
Your wife scares her.

05:20.353 --> 05:22.354
