Mmm.

05:23.556 --> 05:25.691
<i>That day, my father finally</i>
<i>got to do something</i>

05:25.693 --> 05:29.494
<i>he had been waiting</i>
<i>for since the day</i>
<i>he got married..</i> .

05:29.496 --> 05:30.762
<i>Be right!</i>

05:30.764 --> 05:32.064
(SINGSONG) It's you!

05:32.066 --> 05:33.532
What?
You heard me.

05:33.534 --> 05:37.569
It's not me
that's the problem.
It's you!

05:37.571 --> 05:38.670
What did I do?

05:38.672 --> 05:41.073
Oh. You scare the woman.

05:41.075 --> 05:41.673
Scare her but good.

05:41.675 --> 05:45.377
That is ridiculous.
I have never been
anything but cordial to her.

05:45.379 --> 05:46.111
