the back.

05:58.759 --> 06:03.328
And then he drove back
and picked up our old sink.

06:03.330 --> 06:03.962
You're welcome.

06:03.964 --> 06:06.832
Explain it any way
you want to, Bevy.

06:06.834 --> 06:09.801
That woman no likey you.

06:09.803 --> 06:12.504
<i>But the idea of someone</i>
<i>not liking my mom</i>

06:12.506 --> 06:13.305
