06:13.307 --> 06:17.609
<i>Beverly Goldberg</i>
<i>prided herself on</i>
<i>being loved by all.</i>

06:17.611 --> 06:20.746
<i>And she couldn't have it</i>
<i>any other way.</i>

06:22.248 --> 06:24.049
