burn period. So...

06:44.605 --> 06:45.804
Oh, good stuff,
good stuff.

06:45.806 --> 06:48.807
Listen, I feel
like we got off
on the wrong foot,

06:48.809 --> 06:50.742
and I know we're gonna
be great friends.

06:50.744 --> 06:54.146
So, please come over
for a barbecue.

06:54.148 --> 06:56.882
(CHUCKLES)
Sure. Sure.
I'll let you know.

06:56.884 --> 06:59.050
Now? Okay, uh,
how about Saturday?

06:59.052 --> 07:00.519
